description:
Subjects Addressed: (1) “Above all, taking the shield of faith, wherewith ye shall be able to quench all the fiery darts of the wicked.” Ephesians 6:16. Discover the connection between the first four parts of God’s armor (0:38)
(2) “The world is stirred with the spirit of war. The prophecy of the eleventh chapter of Daniel has nearly reached its complete fulfillment. Soon the scenes of trouble spoken of in the prophecies will take place.” {9T 14.2}  (7:25)
(3) When the King of the North, the Papacy, is about to return to world dominance, having its deadly wound healed, it will return with “chariots, horsemen, and many ships (Daniel 11:40). These items represent military and economic might. "America is a great power - today probably the only superpower. We accept that," Vladimir Putin said at the St Petersburg International Economic Forum. (10:34)
(4) The European Union is setting up a global military force. Through the lenses of Bible prophecy we understand that this global army will be used by the Papacy to accomplish her agenda, as Emperor Justinian of Rome gave to Popery world dominion and a military army. “Just Days After Brexit, EU Releases Plan For Further Expansion, An EU Army”  “Obama Administration and UN Announce Global Police Force to Fight ‘Extremism’ In U.S.” “Has Britain avoided a ‘European superstate’? France and Germany ‘draw up plans to morph EU countries into one with control over members’ armies and economies’” “Turkish President: Unless all governments and the entire mankind join forces in the fight against terrorism, much worse things than what we fear to imagine today will come true.” (15:04)
(5) The King of the North and his allies will control the wealth of the world. Putin: Blew the whistle on the U.S. “The world is seeing ever-stronger competition for resources, and some players try to disregard all the rules, Russian President Vladimir Putin has said, adding that potential for conflict is growing worldwide. According to the Russian president, the actions of NATO are aimed at upsetting the balance of power…We are noticing persistent efforts by certain partners to maintain a monopoly on geopolitical dominance. They use their centuries of experience in suppressing, weakening, pitting their rivals against each other, as well as modern political, economic, financial, and informational methods,” he said. The examples of such methods are “interference in the domestic politics of other countries, provoking regional conflicts and triggering so-called ‘color revolutions,’” Putin added. The Russian president believes that, at times, "terrorists, fundamentalists, far-right nationalists and even neo-fascists" are used as henchmen in achieving those goals.” (31:13)
(6) The crisis that God’s commandment-keeping people will encounter will be similar to the law being proposed in Russia. “Russia's Proposed Law: No Evangelizing Outside of Church”  “Christians in Russia won’t be allowed to email their friends an invitation to church or to evangelize in their own homes if Russia’s newest set of surveillance and anti-terrorism laws are enacted. The proposed laws, considered the country’s most restrictive measures in post-Soviet history, place broad limitations on missionary work, including preaching, teaching, and engaging in any activity designed to recruit people into a religious group. To share their faith, citizens must secure a government permit through a registered religious organization, and they cannot evangelize anywhere besides churches and other religious sites. The restrictions even apply to activity in private residences and online.” (36:50)
(7) Satan’s fiery darts will be thrown at God’s people who have on the first three parts of God’s armor. Satan’s fiery darts and arrows are Persecutions; False accusations, black-balls.  (44:00)
(8) Satan’s fiery darts and arrows are witchcraft. Discover how Satan worked through Balaam to remove God’s shield from around the Hebrews just before they crossed over into the earthly promised land of Canaan. Satan is using SDA ministers and leaders to remove God’s shield from around SDAs in these last days. (52:05)
